headline: OREO Cakesters Expands Lineup with New Double Chocolate Flavour and Limited-Time Soft Factory Experience
summary: OREO Cakesters is turning up the indulgence with the launch of OREO Cakesters Double Chocolate, a rich new flavour joining the brand's soft-baked lineup. To add to the celebration OREO is launching the OREO Cakesters Soft Factory, a limited-time immersive consumer experience taking place in the CF Toronto Eaton Centre from January 28 to February 1.

headline: Sweet Meets Salty: RITZ™ Drizzled Minis Arrive in Canada
summary: RITZ™, the iconic buttery cracker brand known for turning everyday snacking into something special, is introducing RITZ™ Drizzled Minis in Canada - a new sweet-and-salty snack that pairs the brand's signature buttery and salty crunch with a smooth sweet drizzle on top.
